source.@value:
pipeline "Filter valid 5G core syslog"
stage 1 match either
rule "Drop message not containing facility field"
rule "Drop message with facility field other than 'local3'"
end

title.@value: Drop message not containing facility field

source.@value:
rule "Drop message not containing facility field"
when
 !has_field("facility")
then
 drop_message();
end

title.@value: Drop message with facility field other than 'local3'

source.@value:
rule "Drop message with facility field other than 'local3'"
when
 has_field("facility") && $message.facility != "local3"
then
 drop_message();
end
